description	"Sith Trooper

Class: Clone Trooper.
Class Summary: 
A multi-life soldier that blends the use of melee and ranged weapons. 

Default Weaponry:
- Vibro-Weapon *

* Special Weapon Descriptions:
--- Sith Carbine:
- High rate of fire gun based on Clone Rifle 
- Has 18 shot clip size

--- Vibro-Weapon
- Defense (1)
- Can use Yellow w/Vibrosword or Staff w/Vibro Double-Blade
- Melee weapon based on Lightsaber
- Deals reduced damage
- Cannot block blaster fire
- Cannot use special attacks
- Can block lightsabers (with reduced block power)
- Vibro Double-Blade has 10% increased swing speed

Default Attributes:
- Assemble
- Reinforcements (1)

The Sith Troopers were the infantry units of the Sith Empire during the Jedi Civil War."